dc_description_s: This data layer represents municipal wards in Wisconsin in 2021. [This data has been collected as part of the 2021 local redistricting process in the State of Wisconsin. Data was submitted to the Legislative Technology Services Bureau through the WISE-LR (Wisconsin Shape Editor for Local Redistricting) application between August 2021 and February 2022.
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For additional information and most current data, please visit https://gis-ltsb.hub.arcgis.com/.
